      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable scratches, scuffs, and areas of paint wear beyond normal use, though there are no major structural dents. The interior has visible wear including fading, minor tears, and some soiling on the upholstery. Mechanically the car is functional, but it will likely need some attention over time. Sold as-is.",
